description.text: Well maintained two 4 unit buildings located in highly desirable Hancock Park and Koreatown. These two parcels, strategically positioned on a corner lot, offer an outstanding investment opportunity and are to be sold in conjunction with 4754 Elmwood (5522-031-022) Each unit is equipped with its own laundry hook-up, adding to their desirability.

description.text:
Elegance and luxury in Hancock Park residence provides abundant space for both relaxation and entertainment. Marble flooring and a sweeping staircase set the tone for the refined aesthetic found throughout. Formal living room, elegant dining area, a stylish chef's kitchen, custom cabinetry, and a spacious island. The master suite is a private retreat, featuring a generous bedroom space with his and her walk-in closet. cozy fireplace, and en-suite bathroom. Each of the additional bedrooms offers its own ample closet space and en-suite bathrooms, The 
outdoor oasis is an entertainer's dream, landscaped backyard with lush greenery, hosting gatherings with a built-in BBQ area, enjoying the California sunshine. There is a spacious backyard where you can build a swimming pool according to your desires. Guest house with own kitchen and bathroom. Situated in prestigious Hancock Park, this home is nestled within a desirable neighborhood renowned for its tree-lined streets, and strong sense of community.
